Van-Ho Nguyen (M.A.) received the B.S. degree in Management Information System (MIS) from the Faculty of Information Systems, University of Economics and Law (VNU–HCM), Vietnam, in 2015, and the Master’s degree in MIS from the University of Economics Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, in 2020. He is currently a Lecturer at the Faculty of Information Systems, University of Economics and Law, VNU-HCM. His current research interests include business analytics, business intelligence, data analytics, and machine learning.
