Thanh Ho (Ph.D.) received M.S. degree in Information Technology from University of Information Technology, VNU–HCM, Vietnam in 2009 and Ph.D. degree in Information Technology from University of Information Technology, VNU-HCM, Vietnam in 2018. He is currently an Associate Professor, Senior Lecturer in Faculty of Information Systems, University of Economics and Law, VNU–HCM, Vietnam. His research interests are data mining, data analytics, business intelligence, social network analysis, machine learning and big data.
